videos.description: On the third play of the game, Marshall QB Isaiah Green's pass was intercepted by UCF's Richie Grant and returned back for a 39-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Grant gets a 39-yard pick-6 for UCF

videos.description: UCF's Greg McCrae finds the open gap and rushes in for the 26-yard touchdwon untouched.
videos.headline: McCrae breaks free for a 26-yard TD

videos.description: Marshall's attempt for a lateral play fails when Tre'Mon Morris-Brash interrupts the toss and picks the ball up and runs it 45 yards for the Knights' third touchdown of the quarter.
videos.headline: UCF's Morris-Brash tips the pass, scoops, and scores

videos.description: UCF DB Richie Grant takes an interception to the house early in the first quarter and a little bit later, DL Tre'Mon Morris-Brash finds the end zone on a scoop-and-score.

videos.headline: UCF notches two defensive TDs in first quarter

videos.description: Marshall DB Micah Abraham jumps in front of UCF OB Darriel Mack Jr.'s pass and takes it 75 yards to the house.

videos.headline: Abraham gets Marshall on the board with 75-yard pick-six

videos.description: On 4th-and-7, UCF QB Dillon Gabriel tosses a short pass to RB Otis Anderson, who races 35 yards into the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: UCF turns 4th-down conversion into TD

videos.description: Marshall QB Isaiah Green connects with Willie Johnson on a 70-yard touchdown pass. On UCF's ensuing possession, QB Dillon Gabriel finds Marion Williams for a 75-yard score.

videos.description: Multiple unsportsmanlike penalties are called after another UCF-Marshall scuffle. The Thundering Herd's Darius Hodge gets disqualified to the confusion of Marshall head coach Doc Holliday.
